data.description: This charming two-story traditional home offers a spacious and inviting living space in a fantastic NW area. With four good sized bedrooms and two well-appointed bathrooms, it's perfect to call this your new home. The formal dining room allows ample room for dinner guests or holiday parties! The lovely hardwood floors throughout the home lend a warm and timeless aesthetic. The fenced yard provides both privacy and security, and leads you to the attached garage.  Additionally, the finished lower level offers versatile space for recreation, play room or another family room, making this home a true gem for those seeking space, comfort and style.
